text: Nataliya Kazak (born 4 February 1960) is a Soviet rower. She competed in two events at the 1980 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1960 births Category:Living people Category:Soviet female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of the Soviet Union Category:Rowers at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
